<P>
UB40 Members Deported: Five musicians and two technicians from the British pop 
band UB40 arrested on suspicion of possessing marijuana will be deported from 
the Indian Ocean islands of Seychelles, police said Tuesday. Authorities said 
there was enough evidence to charge the seven, but they had decided to deport 
them instead. UB40 gave a concert Saturday and their performance was described 
by the islands' only newspaper, the Seychelles Nation, as a technical fiasco. 
