PGA CHAMPIONSHIP (GOLF TOURNAMENT); SOUTHERN CHRISTIAN LEADERSHIP CONFERENCE; 
GOLF TOURNAMENTS; PROFESSIONAL GOLFERS ASSOCIATION OF AMERICA; SPONSORS; 
TELEVISION BROADCASTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080190-0041 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 255324 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 1, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
