</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mike Heath, catcher for the Detroit Tigers, was suspended for two games by the 
American League for bumping umpire John Hirschbeck. Heath plans to appeal, and 
can continue to play until a hearing is held. 
</P>
