during the first half of the 94-70 U.S. victory at the Goodwill Games. 
Associated Press; Photo, (San Diego Edition) Brazil's Janet Arcain pulls down a 
rebound in front of Canada Michelle Hendry in the Goodwill Games Tuesday. 
Brazil beat Canada, 78-75. Associated Press 
