<DOCID> 282533 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 1, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
EUGENE L ROBERTS JR 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 4; Financial Desk 
</P>
